---
import Contact from "../components/Contact.astro";

import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<style>
  p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<BaseLayout title="Jacob Packert">
  <h1>Hi! I'm Jacob Packert ✨</h1>

  <section>
    <p>I like tech, urbanism, music and code.</p>
    <p>
      I live in lovely
      <a
        href="https://medium.com/@jacobpackert/why-bicycling-in-copenhagen-is-so-fantastic-ac5e56349df7"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Copenhagen</a
      >, Denmark.
    </p>
    <p>
      I work as a Lead Engineer at <a
        href="https://lego.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">The LEGO Group</a
      >, building cool digital products for grown-ups.
    </p>
    <p>
      I used to work with politics, then I worked with marketing. Some would say
      that's the same thing.
    </p>
    <p>
      Now I write code for a living and build products and websites. For work
      and for fun.
    </p>
    <p>
      I love JavaScript, TypeScript, Node.js and React, and I've built a few
      apps with React Native, for example <a
        href="https://apps.apple.com/dk/app/dr-nyheder/id398346158"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">DR Nyheder</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      I occassionally dabble in Python, and dipping my toes into
      languages like Go, .NET and Rust.
    </p>
  </section>
  <Contact />
</BaseLayout>
